title: Resizable Tiddlers
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The width of each tiddler cam be changed with the <<material-icon "zoom_in">> and <<material-icon "zoom_out">> buttons. The `span` field contains a the grid column width each tiddler. The valid range is from 1 to 12. Tiddlers without a `span` field are rendered at one third of the available column width.